Book-history of Erastus Bingham & Lucinda Gates printed 1977 and Ancestors of the Bingham Fam of Utah Aug 1963.

US Census shows 1850 Weber Utah residence of Erastus(53) and Lucinda(53) Bingham with sons Brigham H(19), Edwin(9), and father-in-Law Thomas Gates(74).  Also, married son Sanford(29) and wife Martha A(18) Bingham with children Sanford(2) and Martha(1).  Includes birthplace of all.
Erastus worked as a farmer with sons Sanford and Edwin.
